# Track only OUR glue: configs, run/plot/parse scripts, READMEs, figures,
# and the SMALL cited run-results. Everything ignored below is re-creatable /
# re-clonable and kept locally only (NOT pushed to GitHub).

# cloned upstream agent source (re-clone on demand)
*/external/
openclaw/tools/
# python virtualenvs (re-install)
*/.venv/
*/.venv_*/
*/venv/
# datasets / large inputs
*/data/
*/datasets/
*/results/
*/trajectories/
*/*.log

# large / scratch run outputs  — but KEEP the small CITED results:
#   inference/runs/sync (entropy-gating), openclaw/runs (passes_*, perf_cat_prod),
#   bigcodebench/runs (agentic*)  -> these are intentionally NOT ignored.
swe_agent/runs/
inference/runs/phase1/
inference/runs/ncu/

**/__pycache__/

# secrets (NEVER commit — contain live API keys)
.env
*.env
swe_agent/.env
